                    "value": "<p>caused by the raging Epidemic of last summer.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I have the honor to remain with sentiments of\n                                        esteem</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(5)\">Your Very Obt Sevt</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(6)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">L. Cohn</persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(6)\">Secretary H. B. A.</p>\n                              <div>\n                                        <p>\n                                                  <ref target=\"Occident_PDFs/Occ_6_2.pdf\">The above\n                                                  text refers to Occident Volume 6 No. 2 page 107.\n                                                  Click here to view.</ref>\n                                        </p>\n                              </div>\n                    </body>\n          </text>\n</TEI>"
